<p class="kicker">Web / APIs</p>
<h1>TYPO3 – Content Management System for Your Individual Website Design</h1>
<p>Building online shops requires complex customisations that are individual for each business model. We use TYPO3 to set up the details of your online shop according to menu items, design details and functions. We particularly appreciate the speed with which we can implement individual development steps and make them visible for your target groups.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>TYPO3 – Briefly Explained by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>TYPO3, as software, manages various areas of your online shop. These work optimally with the features of Shopware 6 as your fast, adaptable and reliable shop system. In addition, TYPO3 features can be integrated without your own programme code using extensions. For this development step, we are experts in the meta-language TypoScript, which is indispensable for setting up your online shop. You can then manage your backend with TYPO3 and constantly update the frontend — the publicly visible side of your online shop — for the best possible user view.</p>

<h2>Our Development Services with TYPO3 for Your Online Shop</h2>
<p>These detailed services are included in TYPO3 as a development component for e-commerce by Hob by Horse:</p>
<ul>
<li>UI and UX development</li>
<li>Extension development</li>
<li>Responsive HTML implementation</li>
<li>Interface connection to third-party systems</li>
</ul>
<p>So that your company can subsequently work with the developed components itself, we offer intensive training workshops for your IT managers. Since requirements constantly change with market conditions and target group needs, ongoing optimisations as your development partner remain our long-term task for the success of your online shop.</p>

<h2>Industry Relevance of Developments and Connections with TYPO3</h2>
<p>All e-commerce industries require well-structured websites that are easy to use and excel with a logical design. Such features are already standard in the automotive industry and the wide spectrum of fashion and lifestyle in the technological competition. Your business model becomes unique when we create digital systems for tomorrow's trends using our know-how, the globally innovative Shopware 6 shop system, and components like TYPO3. Then your hotel business or country inn in the hospitality industry is just as successfully positioned as a large insurance service provider or real estate company.</p>

<h2>Benefits of TYPO3 from Hob by Horse for Your Target Groups</h2>
<p>With our support, you position your online shop with individual campaigns and strategic online marketing ever more precisely at your target groups. For example, we can integrate your individual templates with TYPO3 in such a way that you convince B2B trading partners with expertise and make them curious with market-relevant advertising. The management of multilingual websites enables easy understanding of your page content for B2C consumers. Maintaining your online shop with TYPO3 is possible without programming knowledge.</p>
<p>Would you like to connect third-party systems to your shop system with TYPO3 or use your individual templates for the development of a brilliantly functioning online shop? You can reach Hob by Horse by phone and also arrange an appointment immediately by email!</p>
</div></div>
